      "text": " Another interesting inequality of mixed volumes involving  $\\Delta_n$  was derived by I. Soprunov and A. Zvavitch (see [\\[SZ16\\]](#page-1-1)), using the Bernstein-Kushnirenko-Khovanskii theorem (see [\\[Ber75\\]](#page-1-1), [\\[Kho78\\]](#page-1-1), [\\[Ku\\]](#page-1-1)), and an inequality from real algebraic geometry called Bezout inequality:",
